{"date": "2026-05-07", "format": "carousel", "pillar": "vater-sohn", "image_urls": ["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/darioprenzyna17-cmd/montagsluege-autopilot/main/assets/carousels/w1-d4-vater-sohn/slide-1.png", "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/darioprenzyna17-cmd/montagsluege-autopilot/main/assets/carousels/w1-d4-vater-sohn/slide-2.png", "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/darioprenzyna17-cmd/montagsluege-autopilot/main/assets/carousels/w1-d4-vater-sohn/slide-3.png", "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/darioprenzyna17-cmd/montagsluege-autopilot/main/assets/carousels/w1-d4-vater-sohn/slide-4.png", "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/darioprenzyna17-cmd/montagsluege-autopilot/main/assets/carousels/w1-d4-vater-sohn/slide-5.png"], "caption": "Dein Vater wäre nicht stolz.\n\nAber er hat's auch nie geschafft, der Mann zu werden, den du brauchst. Du wirst zu dem Mann, dem du als Kind nicht vertraut hast.\n\nWas bricht die Kette? Schreib's in die DM.\n\n—\n#mindset #mannsein #stoiker #montagsluege #generation", "status": "posted", "posted_at": "2026-05-07T11:00:00", "media_id": "17861354673583304", "permalink": "https://www.instagram.com/p/DYCBnS4F-om/"}
